            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Jagwanti Jagbir"
          },
          "datePublished": "2023-03-29",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Hi All,\nI picked Ajanta public school to enroll my daughter last year after doing some analysis based on online information I gathered hence I thought of sharing the same as my ward completes one year here, I hope its helpful to others.\n\nI can say that I made a perfect choice as APS has vision for overall development of kids, give them all options to flourish.\n\nTeachers here are very supportive, special thanks to Ms. Pooja khurana for giving more than 100% to support parents and making our kids love school and school culture which is very critical.\n\nI think I will highly recommend this school to all parents who want there kid's overall development.\n\nThanks,\nJagwanti\n(Navisha's Mom)",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
